title: The definitions in a namespace can be defined in more than one place.
pid: 8a68204f-249a-47bf-8378-21d5c6ae2a3a
body: |2-
  e.g. this defines Data.Customer and Data.Order

  Namespace Data
      Class Customer
      End Class
  End Namespace

  Namespace Data
      Class Order
      End Class
  End Namespace
